    • prepareValue

      protected void prepareValue(StringBuilder handlers)
      Performs any pre-processing on the value property before printing it. The default behavior is to append an asterik inside a span tag with a CSS class attribute of getRequiredStyleClass(), if the required property is set.
      Parameters:
      handlers - The StringBuilder that output will be appended to.
